  "texts": [
    "However, OTFS is inferior to OFDM in computational complexity owing to the complicated modulation approach.",
    "Parameter estimationIn addition to waveform design, parameter estimation is also an important issue in communicationcentric ISAC systems.",
    "Sturm et al. [101] proposed a joint range and Doppler estimation scheme for the OFDM-based ISAC by exploiting its signal structure.",
    "Similarly, Liu et al. [160] developed an OFDMbased super-resolution range and velocity estimation method by exploiting its translational invariance property in the frequency and pulse domains.",
    "Raviteja et al. [168] developed an OTFS-based matched filter to estimate the range and velocity of the target."
  ],
